{
  "stem": "15576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, this is going to take a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Germans came in-- when the Russians came in-- when the Russians left, rather, I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the German's came in--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was, I think, 19-- 1939 or 1940.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember the exact-- I don't remember the exact date.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when the war started with Russia, 1939, I think, it started.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poland.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1941.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was-- I wasn't sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some people tried to run away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know where to go or what to do, so we stayed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it became very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Ukrainians had their run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did whatever they wanted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would break in during the-- break in during the night and take stuff out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the morning, the police came to investigate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And during the night, they were the same people that we actually saw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Beatings started.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "One thing happened almost right away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were some Russian-- Russians lost their group to go back to Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were about 12 or 13 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And one-- one of them was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had a cousin living-- it was near a cemetery that she lived.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they came on a Friday, maybe, she can give them some food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And with that, what she had, she put in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Around 3 o'clock in the afternoon, the police-- I forgot to tell you one thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "To us, the Russians didn't come in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The Hungarians came in first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they went to the Hungarian government, and they told them-- they-- they were working, together, with Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Even Jews-- Jews were in there-- that army-- just to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Anyway, they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They took all the man into the police stations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they were beating them something awful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
